body:
Hello!Thanks for showing interest in my thread!
Im a loyal League player,but recently 3-4 days(or even more) I`m finding myself to have sudden lag spikes,they`re not bit like thousands or hundreds,but it really influences the gameplay.
1. Let me explain now: The game starts on summoners,or howling abyss and after like 1 minute into the game,or even 2 minutes,when minions are already fighting I get a lag spike when I use an ability,it MIGHT not be EVERYTIME I use an ability but 90% of the time it is.As the game gets going 15+ mins,it starts to be really annoying that when I use Lissandras E to escape,in the instace that I press it,my MS goes from 40 to 120-100 in a second,not allowing me to reactivate the spell,because of the lag-because of which I die.Its really frustrating,I just want to know if anyone else is experiencing this or If this is my ISP`s fault or its from the patch(Rito pls).Thanks for reading! Have a wonderful day y`all!{{item:3073}}
